GBirthday is a birthday reminder application that helps you to remember
your contacts' birthdays. It can be used with Evolution Contacts,
Thunderbird/Icedove Lightning and Sunbird/Iceowl Events, CVS-files,
MySQL-Databases. It puts an icon on notification area which will blink
when there is any of your contacts' birthday today. You can also check
if there is any of your contacts' birhday on next days.
